Istanbul Airport Mobile App: Passenger Journey
Project Overview As one of the world’s largest aviation hubs, Istanbul Airport requires more than just a flight tracker; it demands a comprehensive digital companion. I designed this mobile experience to cover the entire "Home-to-Gate" journey, transforming a potentially stressful environment into a seamless, high-end user experience.

1. The Home-to-Gate Experience
This feature serves as the core of the application, guiding passengers from their doorstep to the aircraft door.

Contextual Flight Tracking: Dynamic updates on gate assignments, boarding status, and baggage carousel information delivered via push notifications.

Smart Carpark Management: Integrated reservation system and a "Find My Car" feature, ensuring that the transition from vehicle to terminal is frictionless.

Indoor Explore & Navigation
Navigating 76 million square meters of terminal space was a primary UX challenge.

Intuitive Mapping: High-fidelity indoor maps featuring "blue-dot" navigation to guide users to their gate or specific points of interest.

Discovery Layer: A categorized directory for food, beverage, and retail stores, allowing passengers to explore terminal offerings based on their proximity.

2. Istanbul Airport Chatbot: AI-Powered Concierge
UI Design & Interaction Designed to act as a digital assistant for domestic and international travelers, the Chatbot UI focuses on rapid information retrieval in a mobile-first format.

Targeted Assistance: Provides instant guidance on flight gates, lounge locations, and fast-track zones.

Conversational Flow: Utilizing quick-reply buttons and rich media cards to display shop menus or service details, reducing the need for manual typing in a busy airport setting.

3. İGA Pass: Premium Loyalty & Subscription Services
E-commerce & Subscription UI The redesign of the İGA Pass platform focused on making luxury airport services accessible and easy to purchase.

Premium Service Showcase: A visually driven interface for high-value services including Lounge access, Buggy transfers, Fast Track, and Meet & Greet assistance.

Conversion-Optimized Monetization: * Instant Bundles: Designed for one-time travelers seeking immediate comfort.

Subscription Models: A clear, tiered UI for monthly and yearly memberships, targeting frequent flyers and corporate accounts.